---
description: "Expo React-Native rules"
globs:
  - mobile/**/*.tsx
---

• Functional components with React 18 JSX; no classes.  
• Use `expo-notifications` for reminders; schedule with `date-fns-tz`.  
• Store persistent settings via `AsyncStorage` wrapper `useSettingsStore`.  
• Do not create nested Expo apps; check `app.json` before scaffolding.
